snippet: Tayler Hill tied a career high with 16 points to help the Washington Mystics defeat the Liberty, 70-52, and clinch the third playoff seed in the Eastern Conference.
abstract: Washington Mystics defeat  New York Liberty, 70-52, and secure the third playoff seed in the Eastern Conference of WNBA.
lead_paragraph: Tayler Hill tied a career high with 16 points to help the Washington Mystics defeat the Liberty, 70-52, and clinch the third playoff seed in the Eastern Conference.
